Starting point for hackers:
http://soundcloud.com/developers

Play with our console and explore available data:
http://soundcloud.com/developers/console

Get started right away with our special Public API Key (read only):
"guardian-hack-day"
(e.g.: http://api.soundcloud.com/users/forss.json?consumer_key=guardian-hack-day)

To earn write access, please register your own app on SoundCloud:
http://soundcloud.com/you/apps/new

Our wiki on github:
https://github.com/soundcloud/api/wiki/


Feel free to get in touch with us if you have any additional questions!
